<h2>Bruising or discoloration, Itching or burning and Vaginal dryness</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms bruising or discoloration, itching or burning and vaginal dryness including Bruise or contusion, Hematoma, and Perimenopause.</p>
<p>There  are 7 conditions  associated with bruising or discoloration, itching or burning and vaginal dryness. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
</div>
