</li>
<li class="bg"><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e7b94&amp;bpid[0]=35&amp;sid[0]=45&amp;bpid[1]=35&amp;sid[1]=129&amp;bpid[2]=35&amp;sid[2]=521" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Perimenopause</a><p>Perimenopause is a transitional stage before menopause, causing irregular periods, hot flashes, and more. </p>
